# Taxon

Tools for a zettelkasten

## Make Index

`TaxonCL make-index --title "Recipes" --note-folder ~/Documents/Zettlekasten/ --start-note 0g --output-file-title 0g`

Generates indexes by using the note IDs (taken from the filename) for ordering and indendation, e.g:



```md
- Zettelkasten  [[4c]]
    - Principle of Atomicity [[4c1]]
        - Evergreen Note [[4c1a]]
        - Transient notes [[4c1b]]
    - Zettelkastens Suck When They're Noisy [[4c2]]
- Note taking system [[4d]]
    - Note taking [[4d1]]
        - Writing [[4d1a]]
    - Note Taking App [[4d2]]
- PARA [[4e]]
    - Digital Organisation System [[4e1]]
    - Tiago Forte [[4e2]]
- Methods for Creating Note IDs [[4f]]
```

## Swap Links

`TaxonCL swap-links 1f1 1f ~/Documents/Zettlekasten/`

Finds all instances of either link within the notes and swaps them with the other other
